{"id":542,"date":"2026-03-26T08:12:01","date_gmt":"2026-03-26T08:12:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/?p=542"},"modified":"2026-03-26T11:35:04","modified_gmt":"2026-03-26T11:35:04","slug":"communique-de-presse-demande-de-clarification-du-positionnement-politique-dolivier-conte-sur-lunion-des-droites","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/?p=542","title":{"rendered":"Communiqu\u00e9\u00a0: Demande de clarification du positionnement politique d\u2019Olivier Conte sur l\u2019union des droites"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-543 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Nouvelle-image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Nouvelle-image.png 1024w, https:\/\/vesemt.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Nouvelle-image-200x300.png 200w, https:\/\/vesemt.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Nouvelle-image-683x1024.png 683w, https:\/\/vesemt.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Nouvelle-image-768x1152.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\" \/><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Adress\u00e9 \u00e0 :<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">&#8211; Olivier Conte,<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">&#8211; Medias,<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">&#8211; Organisations anti-racistes politiques.<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><!--more--><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">\u00c0 la suite de l\u2019article publi\u00e9 le 23 mars 2026 par La Nouvelle R\u00e9publique, \u00e9voquant l\u2019appartenance du maire de Saint-Pierre-des-Corps, Olivier Conte, au mouvement \u00ab Nouvelle \u00c9nergie \u00bb fond\u00e9 par David Lisnard, nous souhaitons interpeller publiquement l\u2019int\u00e9ress\u00e9 afin d\u2019obtenir une clarification explicite de son positionnement politique.<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Cette demande intervient alors que David Lisnard a encore r\u00e9affirm\u00e9 tr\u00e8s r\u00e9cemment, lors d\u2019une intervention sur BFMTV le 25 mars 2026, son souhait d\u2019une \u201cprimaire ouverte\u201d \u00e0 droite, estimant qu\u2019\u201cune primaire, c\u2019est forc\u00e9ment ouvert, vient qui veut, vote qui veut\u201d et d\u00e9fendant explicitement un p\u00e9rim\u00e8tre incluant des figures situ\u00e9es \u00e0 la droite radicale, telles que celles issues de l\u2019entourage d\u2019\u00c9ric Zemmour ou de Sarah Knafo. \u00bb <\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Dans ce contexte, nous demandons \u00e0 Olivier Conte de pr\u00e9ciser sans ambigu\u00eft\u00e9 :<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">S\u2019il soutient cette ligne politique port\u00e9e par \u00ab Nouvelle \u00c9nergie \u00bb ;<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">S\u2019il consid\u00e8re acceptable le principe d\u2019une union des droites incluant des formations ou personnalit\u00e9s class\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u2019extr\u00eame droite ;<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Et, plus largement, quelle est sa position personnelle sur une \u00e9ventuelle recomposition politique nationale impliquant ces forces.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Nous rappelons que VESEMT condamne sans r\u00e9serve toute tentative d\u2019alliance ou de normalisation de l\u2019extr\u00eame droite dans le paysage politique fran\u00e7ais. Une telle orientation constituerait une rupture grave avec les principes r\u00e9publicains fondamentaux et participerait \u00e0 donner \u00e0 une \u00e9ventuelle majorit\u00e9 nationale une coloration id\u00e9ologique extr\u00e9miste, voire dangereusement proche de logiques que nous combattons fermement.<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\"><b>Au regard des responsabilit\u00e9s locales exerc\u00e9es par Olivier Conte, cette clarification appara\u00eet indispensable pour garantir la transparence d\u00e9mocratique vis-\u00e0-vis des citoyens et l&rsquo;apolitisme de la liste qu&rsquo;il entend conduire<\/b>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Nous restons dans l\u2019attente d\u2019une prise de position publique claire et rapide, et samedi matin, lors de l&rsquo;installation du Conseil Municipal est pour nous une attente forte.<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\"><strong>Saint-Pierre-des-Corps, le 26 mars 2026<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Contacts presse :<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Abd-El-Kader A\u00cfT-MOHAMED 07 77 96 61 40 (<a href=\"mailto:vesemet@gmail.com\">vesemet@gmail.com<\/a>)<\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Signataires :<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Vivre Ensemble Solidaires en M\u00e9tropole Tourangelle\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/\">https:\/\/vesemt.org<\/a> <\/span><\/p>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Source : <\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Intervention David Lisnard sur BFM TV le 25\/03\/2026<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p align=\"JUSTIFY\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial Naarow;\">Article de La Nouvelle R\u00e9publique, \u00e9dition du 23 mars 2026.\u00a0: \u00ab\u00a0Olivier Conte Confirme \u00e0 Saint-Pierre-des-Corps<\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Adress\u00e9 \u00e0 : &#8211; Olivier Conte, &#8211; Medias, &#8211; Organisations anti-racistes politiques.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"colormag_page_container_layout":"default_layout","colormag_page_sidebar_layout":"default_layout","footnotes":""},"categories":[38],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-542","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-saint-pierre-des-corps"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/542","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=542"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/542\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":548,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/542\/revisions\/548"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=542"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=542"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=542"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}